description: http://anidb.net/ch5758 [Momozono Love] is a 14-year-old student at Yotsuba Junior High School who tends to care more for others than for herself. One day she visits a show of the famous dance unit Trinity and decides to become a dancer, too. At the same event, subordinates of the Labyrinth Kingdom show up wanting to collect the unhappiness of the audience. Love gets the power to change into http://anidb.net/ch5761 [Cure Peach] and fights against them. Soon after, she is joined by her good friends http://anidb.net/ch5759 [Miki], who is http://anidb.net/ch5762 [Cure Berry], and http://anidb.net/ch5760 [Inori], who becomes http://anidb.net/ch5763 [Cure Pine].

REGULAR.description: The fairy elder goes to Pretty Cure Forest and prays in the corresponding temple. Lightning strikes the temple and the elder sees four Pickruns flying away. Meanwhile, in the human world, Love goes to the dance unit Trinity event. On the way, a huge monster called a Nakewameke appears, ruining the event. Love tries to protect her idol, Miyuki. Suddenly, the Pirun appears and goes to her mobile phone, transforming her into Cure Peach and allowing her to battle the monster.

titles.title: Freshly-Picked Fresh! Cure Peach Is Born!!
Mogitate Fresh! Cure Peach Tanjou!!
もぎたてフレッシュ! キュアピーチ誕生!!

REGULAR.description: After the battle, Tart appears in front of Love. According to Tart, she is the legendary warrior, Precure, who has to stop Mobius` ambition. Love is shocked upon hearing this. Tart tells Love that they need to find the other three Precure. Meanwhile, Miki encounters a vending machine-like Nakewameke, and transforms into Cure Berry through the use of the Blun to protect her brother.

titles.title: Freshly-Gathered Fresh! Cure Berry Is Born!!
Tsumitate Fresh! Cure Berry Tanjou!!
つみたてフレッシュ! キュアベリー誕生!!

REGULAR.description: Inori has begun feeling a bit left out because she is too shy to dance with Love and Miki. She finds comfort in taking care of a little boy`s dog. When the dog becomes a Nakewameke, Inori gains the ability to transform into Cure Pine through the Kirun.

titles.title: Freshly-Harvested Fresh! Cure Pine Is Born!!
Toretate Fresh! Cure Pine Tanjou!!
とれたてフレッシュ! キュアパイン誕生!!

REGULAR.description: Chiffon goes missing and causes a lot of trouble in town, it`s up to the girls to find her.

titles.title: Chiffon Is a Lost Child? The Town Is in an Uproar!!
Chiffon ga Maigo? Machijuu Mou Oosawagi!!
シフォンが迷子? 町中もう大騒ぎ!!

REGULAR.description: Three boys from Love`s school go on a triple date with the girls. Wester makes a panda cart become a Nakewameke and causes chaos, that is unless the girls stop him.

titles.title: My Heart`s Racing at the Amusement Park! Those Trembling Dating Feelings!?
Yuuenchi de Dokidoki! Wakuwaku Date Kibun!?
遊園地でドキドキ! ワクワクデート気分!?

REGULAR.description: Love buys hamburgers at the shop where her mother works. After Love finishes cooking the hamburgers disappear due to Souler`s Nakewameke. Later on, the same Nakewameke erases the Cures` mothers, and it is up to the Cures to finish off the Nakewameke.

titles.title: Kieta Hamburger! Daisuki na Mono o Mamore!!
The Missing Hamburger! Protect Your Favourite Things!!
消えたハンバーグ! 大好きなものを守れ!!

REGULAR.description: Setsuna goes to the town centre to meet Love according to fortune telling. Love is playing Lucky Draw in town when Setsuna meets her. She asked Love to give a tour of the town, on the way, she tries to steal Love`s Linkrun.

titles.title: Setsuna and Love: The Clover of Friendship!
Setsuna to Love: Yuujou no Clover!
せつなとラブ 友情のクローバー!

REGULAR.description: Love accidentally forgot to refil the Cure Vitan, Chiffon`s food, and lost the contact to get more. Chiffon cannot get food from Linkrun, so Love has to cook something for Chiffon. Cure Peach`s new weapon, the Peach Rod, first appears in this episode.

titles.title: Chiffon Dai Pinch! Peach no Atarashii Chikara!!
Chiffon`s in Big Trouble! Peach`s New Powers!!
シフォン大ピンチ! ピーチの新しい力!!

REGULAR.description: Miki wants to be a famous top model around the world. One day she got the chance for the audition; if she passes the audition, she can get the chance to be a model overseas. She is very happy, but at the same time, she thinks of Love and Inori, because if she passes, she has to say farewell to them. She is puzzled when she realizes that she has to quit dance and Pretty Cure in order to fulfill her dream.

titles.title: Miki no Yume: Watashi Precure Yameru!!
Miki`s Dream: I`m Leaving Pretty Cure!
美希の夢 私プリキュアやめる!!

REGULAR.description: Inori is afraid of ferrets, so she dare not to approach Tart. One day, from Souler`s Nakewameke they swap bodies and it is up to the girls to stop him.

titles.title: Tarte ga Inori de Inori ga Tarte!?
Tarte is Inori, Inori is Tarte!?
タルトが祈里で祈里がタルト!?

REGULAR.description: The girls come late to a dance session. Miyuki gets angry at this and she won`t teach the girls dancing anymore.

titles.title: Miyuki no Ikari! Mou Dance wa Oshienai!?
Miyuki`s Anger! She Won`t Teach Dancing Anymore!?
ミユキの怒り! もうダンスは教えない!?

REGULAR.description: Wester turns one of Love`s dad`s wigs into a Nakewameke, which gives everyone in Clover Town Street weird hairstyles.instead of what westar`s wished,the children is happy,though.

titles.title: Let`s Transform! The Fringy Tactic!!
Minna de Henshin! Fusafusa Daisakusen!!
みんなで変身! フサフサ大作戦!!

REGULAR.description: When Chiffon falls ill, Inori is tasked with nursing her back to health. Cure Pine`s new weapon, the Pine Flute, makes its debut.

titles.title: Chiffon Is Sick!? Pine`s New Power!!
Chiffon ga Byouki!? Pine no Atarashii Chikara!!
シフォンが病気!? パインの新しい力!!

REGULAR.description: Now that Chiffon is able to talk, she tells of four special Pickruns. These give the girls the ability to become Pretty Cure and grant them powers. Three of them, the Pirun, the Blun, and the Kirun, are found. All that remains is the Akarun, a red Pickrun...

titles.title: 4 Ninme no Precure!? Akarun o Sagase!!
4人目のプリキュア!? アカルンを探せ!!
The Fourth Pretty Cure!? Search for Akarun!!

REGULAR.description: Love meets with Setsuna once again. Setsuna learns that Love truly trusts her as a friend.

titles.title: Setsuna and Love: The Heart That Cares Each Other.
Setsuna to Love: Aite o Omoiyaru Kokoro
せつなとラブ 相手を思いやる心!

REGULAR.description: It`s time for the Culture Festival in Love`s school. Love and Daisuke has a fight during school. When Love gets trapped inside the school with Daisuke, they have to work together to escape the Nakewameke.

titles.title: Culture Festival of Terror! Echoing Footsteps on School at Night!!
Kyoufu no Bunkasai! Yoru no Gakkou ni Hibiku Ashioto!!
恐怖の文化祭! 夜の学校に響く足音!!

REGULAR.description: Miki is tasked with babysitting Chiffon. Cure Berry`s new weapon, the Berry Sword, makes it first appearance.

titles.title: Chiffon wa Makasete! Berry no Atarashii Chikara!!
Leave It to Chiffon! Berry`s New Power!!
シフォンはまかせて! ベリーの新しい力!!

REGULAR.description: Love and the girls meet a terminally ill girl in a hospital. Having seen Pretty Cure before, the sick girl wishes to meet them.

titles.title: Precure ni Aitai! Chiisana Onnanoko no Negai!!
Want to Meet Pretty Cure! The Little Girl`s Wish!!
プリキュアに会いたい! 小さな女の子の願い!!

REGULAR.description: Mobius, the being running Labyrinth, sees that it`s time to destroy Pretty Cure. He gives Eas a new card, but the card has bad side effects to the user...

titles.title: Arata na Card! Eas no Atarashii Chikara!!
The New Card! Eas` New Power!!
新たなカード! イースの新しい力!!

REGULAR.description: Due to all the training for a dance competition, the girls are worn out and are being slowed down. They have to choose whether to keep dancing or live on being just Pretty Cure.

titles.title: Dance and Pretty Cure... Which to Choose?
Dance to Precure... Dochira o Erabu!?
ダンスとプリキュア... どちらを選ぶ!?

REGULAR.description: The night before the dance competition, the girls are hospitalized due to fatigue. Miyuki realizes that while it`s important to focus on dance, it`s also important to focus on recovery. She soon finds about Pretty Cure, but refuses to become the red Cure.

titles.title: 4-ninme no Precure wa Ansan Ya!!
4人目のプリキュアはあんさんや!!
The Fourth Pretty Cure`s Whereabouts!!

REGULAR.description: After being discharged, the girls believe that Miyuki is the fourth member of Pretty Cure. They go on another search for the Akarun. However, they run into Eas again, who reveals her identity as Setsuna.

titles.title: Setsuna and Love: You Are Eas!?
Setsuna to Love: Anata ga Eas na no!?
せつなとラブ あなたがイースなの!?

REGULAR.description: Setsuna is purified by Cure Peach and becomes something she`d never thought she would become: the red Cure of happiness, Cure Passion.

titles.title: Eas no Saigo! Cure Passion Tanjou!!
The End of Eas! Cure Passion Is Born!!
イースの最期! キュアパッション誕生!!

REGULAR.description: Setsuna, who has just become Cure Passion, doesn`t have a place to go back to. While she`s walking down the street, she meets Love, who`s going to a restaurant with her parents.

titles.title: Setsuna no Kunou: Watashi wa Nakama ni Narenai!
The Passionate Pretty Cure Is Born! My Name Is Cure Passion!
せつなの苦悩 私は仲間になれない!

REGULAR.description: Setsuna is haunted by her past deeds as Eas and must confront them when a doppelganger of Eas attacks the Pretty Cures.

titles.title: Eas Tai Passion!? Watashi wa Umarekawaru!!
Eas vs. Cure Passion!
イース対パッション!? 私は生まれ変わる!!

REGULAR.description: Setsuna feels that she wants to join Clover, the dancing group formed by Love, Miki, and Inori.

titles.title: 4つのハート! 私も踊りたい!!
The Four Hearts! I Also Want to Dance!
Yottsu no Heart! Watashi mo Odoritai!!

REGULAR.description: During the summer festival, the girls meet a comedy duo called Audrey.

titles.title: Natsu Da! Matsuri Da! Audrey!!
The Summer! The Festival! Audrey!!
夏だ! 祭りだ! オードリー!!

REGULAR.description: Remembering the time spent with her grandfather, a Nakewameke causes Love to dream of being reunited with him. However, Love must choose between staying with her grandfather in this dream world or helping her friends defeat the Nakewameke.

titles.title: Precious Memories! Memories of Grandpa!!
Taisetsu na Kioku! Ojii-chan to no Omoide!!
大切な記憶! おじいちゃんとの思い出!!

REGULAR.description: The girls and Tart begin to realize something is up with Kaoru and they investigate.

titles.title: Nazodarake no Otoko! Kaoru-chan no Shoutai!?
The Man of Secrets! Kaoru-chan`s True Self!?
謎だらけの男! カオルちゃんの正体!?

REGULAR.description: One day, Tart starts having stomachaches. Ayumi, Love`s Mother, brings him to Dr. Yamabuki`s, not knowing Tart is actually a fairy from the Sweets Kingdom!

titles.title: Tart Kikiippatsu! Shoutai ga Barechau!?
Tart in Danger! His True Self Exposed!?
タルト危機一髪! 正体がばれちゃう!?

REGULAR.description: The new school term has begun. Love is happy seeing that Setsuna has become popular in Yotsuba Junior High, but Daisuke isn`t happy...

titles.title: Love and Daisuke: The Make Up Strategy!
Love to Daisuke: Nakanaori no Shikata!
ラブと大輔 仲直りのしかた!

REGULAR.description: Tart and Chiffon return to the Sweets Kingdom, and the Cures have accompanied them. That, and they find out Tart is the Prince of the Kingdom and is engaged to a pink ferret named Azukiina. The Clover music box of Happiness debuts in this episode.

titles.title: Goodbye! Tart and Chiffon!!
Sayounara! Tart to Chiffon!!
さようなら! タルトとシフォン!!

REGULAR.description: Miki has trouble fighting an octopus Nakewameke, because she has a fear of octopuses.

titles.title: Miki to Setsuna no Kowaimono!
What Miki and Setsuna are Afraid Of!
美希とせつなのこわいもの!

REGULAR.description: The treasure Infinity makes its appearance, a new villain arrives to aid Moebius, and a whole day gets replayed over and over.

titles.title: Infinity Arawareru! Ashita o Torimodose!!
Infinity Arrives! Reclaim Tomorrow!!
インフィニティ現れる! 明日を取り戻せ!!

REGULAR.description: Chiffon is apparently more powerful than she appears to be like making herself a pickrun,giving the cures a boost of power,and more!

titles.title: Chiffon no Kakusareta Himitsu!
Chiffon`s Hidden Secret!
シフォンの隠された秘密!
A New Enemy! Her Name is Northa!
Arata na Teki! Sono Na wa Northa!!
新たな敵! その名はノーザ!!

REGULAR.description: Pretty Cure get intense training from Miyuki, and Chiffon grants them a new power: the group attack, Lucky Clover Grand Finale.

titles.title: Chiffon o Mamore! Precure no Atarashii Chikara!!
Protect Chiffon! Pretty Cure`s New Power!!
シフォンを守れ! プリキュアの新しい力!!

REGULAR.description: Miki loses the Clover music box by accident and now she must protect it from Labyrinth`s hands.

titles.title: Clover Box o Sagase!!
Find the Clover Box!!
クローバーボックスをさがせ!!

REGULAR.description: Love and Setsuna go to Okinawa on a research trip together with their classmates.

titles.title: Fight the Ban? Okinawan School Trip!
Kenka wa Kinshi? Okinawa Shuugakuryokou!!
ケンカは禁止? 沖縄修学旅行!!

REGULAR.description: Setsuna suspects that something is wrong with Love`s mother, Ayumi, and discovers that Love`s "mother" was a Sorewaatase clone of the real one.

titles.title: Setsuna and Love: Mom is in Danger!
Setsuna to Love: Okaasan ga Abunai!
せつなとラブ お母さんが危ない!

REGULAR.description: Kento invites Inori to a boat party on a ship.

titles.title: Inori and Kento`s Boat Party!
Inori to Kento no Senjou Party!
祈里と健人の船上パーティ!

REGULAR.description: Setsuna is hostage by Northa ,and it`s up to her friends to rescue her from being brainwashed back into Labyrinth!

titles.title: Labyrinth kara no Shoutaijou!
The Invitation from Labyrinth!
ラビリンスからの招待状!

REGULAR.description: The Pretty Cures enter into labyrinth`s base in order to destroy the `fuko gage` as they are fighting against Northa and her tricks.

titles.title: Save the World! Pretty Cure Against Labyrinth!!
Sekai o Sukue! Precure Tai Labyrinth!!
世界を救え! プリキュア対ラビリンス!!

REGULAR.description: Northa comes up with a plan to kidnap Chiffon by distracting Pretty Cure.

titles.title: Ayashiki Kusabue! Ubawareta Chiffon!!
Suspicious Reedpipe! Chiffon is Stolen!!
妖しき草笛! 奪われたシフォン!!

REGULAR.description: Love and her friends decide to save Chiffon but they will have to reveal their identities as Pretty Cure in front of their parents and friends.

titles.title: 4-nin wa Precure! Christmas Eve no Wakare!!
4人はプリキュア! クリスマスイブの別れ!!
We are Four Pretty Cures! Separation in Christmas!!

REGULAR.description: Moebius sends Souler and Wester to defeat Pretty Cure without them knowing that he had something else in mind. Note: This was the first Pretty Cure episode to air in the 2010s.

titles.title: Souler and Wester`s Last Battle!!
Souler to Wester: Saigo no Takatai!!
サウラーとウエスター 最期の戦い!!

REGULAR.description: The denizens of Labyrinth were changed by Tart, Azukina and...donuts!

titles.title: Change the World! The Miracle Donuts!!
Sekai ga Kawaru! Donuts ga Okoshita Kiseki!!
世界が変わる! ドーナツが起こした奇跡!!

REGULAR.description: Things seemed hopeless for Pretty Cure until two new heroes and the people of Labyrinth came to help them.

titles.title: Final Decisive Battle! The Birth of Cure Angel!!
Saishuu Kessen! Cure Angel Tanjou!!
最終決戦! キュアエンジェル誕生!!

REGULAR.description: Moebius isn`t what he seems to be...

titles.title: Odoroki no Shinjitsu! Moebius no Hontou no Sugata!!
The Shocking Truth! Moebius` True Form
驚きの真実! メビウスの本当の姿!!

REGULAR.description: The final battle between Cure Angel and Moebius. Will Pretty Cure be able to save Chiffon and the parallel worlds in time? Anyway, Love, Miki, Inori and Setsuna toward to face for the new future. But, what will happen to Tsubomi and Erika...

titles.title: Egao ga Ippai! Minna de Shiawase Get Da yo!!
So Many Smiles! Everyone Will Get Their Happiness!!
笑顔がいっぱい! みんなで幸せゲットだよ!!
